data.description: Welcome to 16028 Grass Lake Drive, an exquisite ranch style home located in the Carrollwood area of Tampa, FL. Situated on a corner lot, this single level home features solar panels, an open floor plan with a total of 1269 square feet. Step through the front door and find yourself in a bright and airy great room with vaulted ceilings that open to the kitchen and dining area. This home offers a split floor plan, with the primary bedroom and its updated en-suite bathroom located conveniently off the great room. The updated kitchen includes granite countertops and updated cabinets. Recently installed french doors lead to the Florida room with a hot tub. Stunning in ground pool with recently relined fiberglass. Enjoy the convenience of a detached 1-car garage and a screened in front porch. Newer, hurricane rated windows. This property is an excellent value with upgrades throughout and a must-see. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this beautiful home.
